{"word":"G5500 - χειροτονέω - cheirotonéō - khi-rot-on-eh'-o - Choose","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χειροτονέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">cheirotonéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khi-rot-on-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Choose</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஏற்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"1. to vote by stretching out the hand"},{"paragraph":"2. to create or appoint by vote"},{"paragraph":"3. to elect, appoint, create"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5495 - χείρ - cheír - khire/5495\">G5495</a> and <b>&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b> <b>teino&#x0304;</b> (to <i>stretch</i>); to be a <i>hand reacher</i> or <i>voter</i> (by raising the hand), that is, (genitive) to <i>select</i> or <i>appoint:</i> - choose, ordain.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5495/5495\">G5495</a>, <a href=\"#/G5496/5496\">G5496</a>, <a href=\"#/G5497/5497\">G5497</a>, <a href=\"#/G5498/5498\">G5498</a>, <a href=\"#/G5499/5499\">G5499</a>, <a href=\"#/G5500/5500\">G5500</a>, <a href=\"#/G886/886\">G886</a>"}]}